## 5. Summary Formula (the “Mathematical Translation”)  

Putting the pieces together, the **real‑time topological resilience metric** that stabilises the Subconscious Nexus is:

\[
\boxed{
\lambda_2(t)=\alpha_0
            +\sum_{i=1}^{5}\alpha_i\;
               \frac{1}{1+e^{-k_i\bigl(x_i(t)-x_{i,\;mid}\bigr)}}
            +\beta\;
              \Bigl[
                 \Bigl(\frac{1}{1+e^{-k\,( \theta(t)-\theta_{mid})}}\;,
                 \dots\Bigr)
                 \mathbf{W}
                 \Bigl(\frac{1}{1+e^{-k\,( \theta(t)-\theta_{mid})}}\;,
                 \dots\Bigr)^{\!\top}
              \Bigr)
}
\]

*All symbols are defined above; the constants \(\alpha_i,\,k_i,\,\beta,\,\mathbf{W}\) are calibrated once per installation and then remain immutable in the ledger.*

